ous to break for us:\r\n\r\n* Drop PHP 5.6 support (fine when we drop it too)\r\n* Introduce namespaced classes e.g. `PHPUnit_Framework_TestCase` -> `PHPUnit\\Framework\\TestCase`\r\n\r\nPHPUnit 7.x (due for Feb 2018 release) also [drops PHP 7.0 support](https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/2473) since it's out of active support at the end of 2017 with PHP 5.6.\r\n\r\nHow do we feel about updating to either PHPUnit 6, or 7 given the PHP version support notes above?\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Pull requests\r\n\r\n- [x] silverstripe/silverstripe-behat-extension#173\r\n- [x] #7716\r\n- [x] silverstripe/silverstripe-versioned#77\r\n- [x] silverstripe/silverstripe-assets#106\r\n- [x] silverstripe/silverstripe-installer#216\r\n- [x] silverstripe/silverstripe-cms#2073\r\n\r\nThese were the modules in the core feature set that needed to be updated to support this change in terms of PHPUnit API changes.\r\n\r\nThe other modules will all need to be updated to increase the minimum PHP version to 7.1, but no test API changes are necessary.\r\n\r\nNote that there's a circular dependency between #7716 and silverstripe/silverstripe-behat-extension#173 :)\r\n  ","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/silverstripe/silverstripe-framework/issues/7653/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/silverstripe/silverstripe-framework/issues/7653/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":1360676636,"node_id":"MDExOkNsb3NlZEV2ZW50MTM2MDY3NjYzNg==","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/events/1360676636","actor":{"login":"sebastianbergmann","id":25218,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI1MjE4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25218?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann","html_url":"https://github.com/sebastianbergmann","followers_ur